        "body": "## Description\r\n\r\nAdds an “Understood” button to the legal warning banner shown in the images step.\r\nOnce acknowledged, the banner is hidden and the user’s choice is persisted using a cookie so it does not reappear on subsequent visits.\r\n\r\nFixes #816\r\n\r\nThis is my first contribution to a large codebase like this, and I used AI assistance during development.  \r\nAll generated suggestions were reviewed to ensure correctness, security, and alignment with the project’s existing patterns.\r\n\r\n> Note: I was not able to run the full application locally due to the hybrid setup of the repository.  \r\n> The change was implemented following existing patterns in the codebase.  \r\n> Please let me know if any adjustments are needed and I’ll be happy to update the PR.\r\n",
